## 8. Children's Privacy

Ultimate Switch does not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13 (or under 16 in the European Economic Area). The App relies on Apple Game Center, which requires users to have an Apple ID and agree to Apple's terms of service.

If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided personal information through the App, please contact us at charliefogg1@gmail.com, and we will take steps to delete such information promptly.

